{"tid":1878501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國牙科協會: 下週將有診所因口罩供應不足停業","createTime":"2020-02-13T15:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T17:35:11.000Z","uid":81045,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe18e55c7eaff3c4ca244a2ddb50925e86592a34","tid":1878501,"uid":81045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Dentists across Britain face closing next week over 'desperate' shortage of masks</span><br />\n<br />\nThe British Dental Association (BDA) said some larger clinics in the UK will <span style=\"color: red;\">run out of masks by the middle of next week</span> and will not be able to treat patients safely under current rules.<br />\n<br />\nA BDA spokesman said more than 50% of face masks used by dentists and other health professionals in the UK are made in China.<br />\n<br />\nExport from Chinese manufacturers have &quot;essentially ceased&quot; due to the virus outbreak.<br />\n<br />\nUK suppliers are restricting the amount that can be ordered, with <span style=\"color: red;\">some suppliers out of stock and others tripling their prices</span>, the spokesman added.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The BDA said similar issues are being seen in New Zealand, Australia and Canada.</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/dentists-across-britain-face-closing-21490372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-news%2Fdentists-across-britain-face-closing-21490372&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=88c15732\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/dentists-across-britain-face-closing-21490372</a><br />\n說好的大貨呢!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e5110e2dee64e6e210d173eff21340cf8acc3e","tid":1878501,"uid":286131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa